### ============================================
### Query Examples
### ============================================

### Get all active carriers
GET {{baseUrl}}/carriers?status=Active
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### Get all inactive carriers
GET {{baseUrl}}/carriers?status=Inactive
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### Search for carriers containing "insurance"
GET {{baseUrl}}/carriers?search=insurance
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### Search for carriers by code
GET {{baseUrl}}/carriers?search=TRAV
Authorization: {{authToken}}
